        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-04-29 12:46:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi,\n\nThis commit aims to extract the outputFullFilePath and outputFilePath fields from ValidationConfigManager in order to improve testability.\n\nThis commit contains multiple modifications resulting from bubbling up the outputFullFilePath static field to where it is actually set. Most of the modifications result from changing the signature of the functions which formerly relied on ValidationConfigManager.getOutputFullFilePath, ValidationConfigManager.setOutputFullFilePath and ValidationConfigManager.getOutputFilePath.\n\nUnfortunately, because this affects many classes and as reformatting is required, this makes this commit an XL one. This work is however critical to solve SDC-2499.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
